| --- | --- | --- |
| **Inside Pod (`exec`)** | **Success** | The Application code is healthy. |
| **`kubectl get ep`** | **Empty** | Fix the **Selector** in your Service YAML. |
| **`minikube ip`** | **Changed** | Update the URL in your browser. |
| **Browser UI** | **404/Timeout** | Check **TargetPort** and **NodePort**. |

